reviewText: The MLS Cup 2007: Houston Dynamo vrs New England Revolution match was a pretty exciting game and had some pretty big twists and turns as the control of the game shifted from New England to Houston. However, this DVD release looks awful. The video transfer is ugly and based on that fact alone it is not worth wasting your time with it.
My boyfriend loved the DVD, he's been a fan of this team for a while. He almost cried when I gave him this for Christmas :D
Relive and enjoy every minute of the Houston Dynamo's second consecutive MLS Championship. Houston Dynamo... the BEST in Texas....and in the MLS!
